If you want the real answer, [Juan Joya Borja](http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/el-risitas-interview-parodies), aka El Risitas, or "The Giggles".

Dunno who it's *supposed* to be at Riot, but there's no lines about how "I wasn't the go-to guy for PvP balance at WoW, that was out of my control", so again, Definitely Not Ghostcrawler.

